{"tid":581532,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"樓市漩渦失控？野村：港現54個金融危機初期訊號","createTime":"2018-03-05T12:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T02:39:35.000Z","uid":174649,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ce3caef4bc3753679c74caaba1631238cfa885e8","tid":581532,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520238623_2f86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520238623_2f86.jpg&h=60d2e336&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近期港滙走弱，分析擔心本港在聯滙制度下，美國加息步伐加快下本港被逼跟隨，連同樓價高企，會為下一場金融危機埋下伏線。英國《每日電訊報》近日有報道引述野村亞洲首席策略師Rob Subbaraman指，本港出現54個反映金融危機的初期警號。<br />\n<br />\n該篇以「樓市熾熱漩渦失控 香港恐成下輪環球危機震央」（Hong Kong risks becoming epicentre of the next global crisis as property boom spirals out of control）為題的報道，引述Subbaraman指，野村預測未來金融危機的模型顯示，本港出現54個反映金融危機的初期警號，較1997至1998年亞洲金融危機時還高。「香港似乎愈來愈容易受到金融壓力打擊，而聯儲局加息周期加快，或會成為潛在觸發點。」他表示。<br />\n<br />\n野村指本港私人部門信貸與GDP的比例，現已高於45%之長期趨勢水平，是全球最高，而該比例高企是泡沫的典型跡象。該行1月初發表報告，指利用去年第二季本港經濟數據計算，本港私人部門信貸與GDP的比例、償債比率、實質樓價及實質有效滙率，均高於長期趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國際清算銀行（BIS）亦指，去年本港信貸規模與其趨勢水平，兩者間之差距升至40點的有紀錄以來最高。上述被稱為「信貸差距」（credit gap）的指標，是BIS用來衡量未來兩至三年銀行危機的指標，倘該指標達到10點，已被視作危機警號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180305/57907434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57907434&d=WlnnxHFi7%2F5XORf1i7aNZDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=c2985bfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57907434&h=dfb6152b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180305/57907434</a>"},{"pid":"856bfda8b2c22a8dba83e3535be2b7737ba4d52f","tid":581532,"uid":126621,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"初期即係有排先爆啦<br />\n此post 已完"},{"pid":"ada91be3ca6d3fdd5f7b7acf4b12d1adfbdc0028","tid":581532,"uid":126621,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:10:13.000Z","msg":"條撚樣年年都講一次<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1507617325347&amp;issue=20171010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1507617325347%26issue%3D20171010&d=WlnnxHFi7%2F5XORf1i7aNZDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=58f16206\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1507617325347%26issue%3D20171010&h=af7ab13f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1507617325347&amp;issue=20171010</a>"},{"pid":"86d13eab1863fa68db9474e2dd8e9eb0f0ba1a23","tid":581532,"uid":42751,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"香港樓價只會升唔會跌"},{"pid":"502f5d64fb20b996e9460ab353bcefdbd0de9d0f","tid":581532,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"咁我都知日本有金粒餐呢樣國技...."},{"pid":"2d1f0710028f928e95b3e7605ba0dd69f5c2325e","tid":581532,"uid":22337,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"86d13eab1863fa68db9474e2dd8e9eb0f0ba1a23","tid":581532,"uid":42751,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"香港樓價只會升唔會跌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n香港最美的是樓價"},{"pid":"0f7f9fb34efd2a5fdb52807451a0da8eb63bc075","tid":581532,"uid":10101,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"我唸佢講個啲指標分析，應該aa未必識睇<br />\n汪敦敬就好啲，都識講m3升，樓價升，仲之點都升升升<br />\n美國加息，帶動經濟好，帶動港樓升，美國縮表，啲錢唔買債,買港樓，帶動港樓升，美股升，財富效應，帶動港樓升，美股跌，啲錢要避險，帶動港樓升，救得一個得一個，唔買樓輸一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e6d4e5c49669b4c4e0d